</P><P ALIGN=LEFT>  </FONT><FONT  COLOR="#400040" SIZE=3 PTSIZE=10><B>Justin can be described in several ways. Dark. Foreboding. Handsome. His facial features are delicate. His skin is fair, leaning a little heavily towards pale, but still mostly fair. He clears six feet with a little bit to spare, weighing 234, he's an athletically built human being. It comes from hopping fences as a kid.   Yes, one might say he is a good looking man. He's not incredibly gorgeous, but he's definately above average. Though it doesnt show when he's fully clothed, behind his right shoulder is "777," as well as a pheonix emerging from flames on his right ankle. Though he's not a superstitious man, he does believe in luck. Pheonixes also fascinate him. The whole idea of birth through death. He likes to think the triple sevens will help him out. Has been contemplating on whether or not to get a "13" tattooed on behind the left or something, but so far hasnt done it. He wears black. and lots of it. While he's riding his motorcycle, he wears black leather pants and jacket. His visored helmet's also black, and it successfully hides his face, except when staring into the sun. Otherwise, he wears a high collared black trenchcoat, a black t-shirt with the head of a howling wolf over the right pec, and black loose-fitting-but-not-baggy  jeans, and black gloves to keep from giving out fingerprints. He hides his switchblade in these jeans.. using it solely when his guns cant be used. Sniper rifle is kept in a black leather briefcase, his pistols <BR>
hidden in his trenchcoat.<BR>
